{"surah":{"number":82,"name":"الإنفطار","englishName":"Al-Infitar","englishTranslation":"The Cleaving","ayahCount":19},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:41.240Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"When the sky breaks apart","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the sky","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱنفَطَرَتْ","english":"(is) cleft asunder","translit":"infaṭarat","root":"فطر"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And when the stars fall, scattering,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْكَوَاكِبُ","english":"the stars","translit":"l-kawākibu","root":"كوكب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱنتَثَرَتْ","english":"scatter","translit":"intatharat","root":"نثر"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And when the seas are erupted","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْبِحَارُ","english":"the seas","translit":"l-biḥāru","root":"بحر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فُجِّرَتْ","english":"are made to gush forth","translit":"fujjirat","root":"فجر"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And when the [contents of] graves are scattered,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْقُبُورُ","english":"the graves","translit":"l-qubūru","root":"قبر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بُعْثِرَتْ","english":"are overturned","translit":"buʿ'thirat","root":"بعثر"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"A soul will [then] know what it has put forth and kept back.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلِمَتْ","english":"Will know","translit":"ʿalimat","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْسٌۭ","english":"a soul","translit":"nafsun","root":"نفس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَدَّمَتْ","english":"it has sent forth","translit":"qaddamat","root":"قدم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَخَّرَتْ","english":"and left behind","translit":"wa-akharat","root":"أخر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"O mankind, what has deceived you concerning your Lord, the Generous,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ","english":"man","translit":"l-insānu","root":"أنس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"What","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَرَّكَ","english":"has deceived you","translit":"gharraka","root":"غرر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِرَبِّكَ","english":"concerning your Lord","translit":"birabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْكَرِيمِ","english":"the Most Noble","translit":"l-karīmi","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Who created you, proportioned you, and balanced you?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"Who","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقَكَ","english":"created you","translit":"khalaqaka","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَسَوَّىٰكَ","english":"then fashioned you","translit":"fasawwāka","root":"سوي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَعَدَلَكَ","english":"then balanced you","translit":"faʿadalaka","root":"عدل"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"In whatever form He willed has He assembled you.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِىٓ","english":"In","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَىِّ","english":"whatever","translit":"ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"صُورَةٍۢ","english":"form","translit":"ṣūratin","root":"صور"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"شَآءَ","english":"He willed","translit":"shāa","root":"شيأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَكَّبَكَ","english":"He assembled you","translit":"rakkabaka","root":"ركب"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"No! But you deny the Recompense.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَلَّا","english":"Nay","translit":"kallā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"But","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبُونَ","english":"you deny","translit":"tukadhibūna","root":"كذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلدِّينِ","english":"the Judgment","translit":"bil-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And indeed, [appointed] over you are keepers,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","english":"And indeed","translit":"wa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","english":"over you","translit":"ʿalaykum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَحَـٰفِظِينَ","english":"(are) surely guardians","translit":"laḥāfiẓīna","root":"حفظ"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Noble and recording;","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كِرَامًۭا","english":"Noble","translit":"kirāman","root":"كرم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَـٰتِبِينَ","english":"recording","translit":"kātibīna","root":"كتب"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"They know whatever you do.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","english":"They know","translit":"yaʿlamūna","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَا","english":"whatever","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَفْعَلُونَ","english":"you do","translit":"tafʿalūna","root":"فعل"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Indeed, the righteous will be in pleasure,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَبْرَارَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-abrāra","root":"برر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَفِى","english":"(will be) surely in","translit":"lafī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"نَعِيمٍۢ","english":"bliss","translit":"naʿīmin","root":"نعم"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And indeed, the wicked will be in Hellfire.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","english":"And indeed","translit":"wa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْفُجَّارَ","english":"the wicked","translit":"l-fujāra","root":"فجر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَفِى","english":"(will be) surely in","translit":"lafī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَحِيمٍۢ","english":"Hellfire","translit":"jaḥīmin","root":"جحم"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"They will [enter to] burn therein on the Day of Recompense,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَصْلَوْنَهَا","english":"They will burn (in) it","translit":"yaṣlawnahā","root":"صلي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(on the) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And never therefrom will they be absent.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَنْهَا","english":"from it","translit":"ʿanhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِغَآئِبِينَ","english":"(will be) absent","translit":"bighāibīna","root":"غيب"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"And what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"And what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","english":"can make you know","translit":"adrāka","root":"دري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Then, what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","english":"can make you know","translit":"adrāka","root":"دري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"It is the Day when a soul will not possess for another soul [power to do] a thing; and the command, that Day, is [entirely] with Allah.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَمْلِكُ","english":"will have power","translit":"tamliku","root":"ملك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نَفْسٌۭ","english":"a soul","translit":"nafsun","root":"نفس"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لِّنَفْسٍۢ","english":"for a soul","translit":"linafsin","root":"نفس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا ۖ","english":"anything","translit":"shayan","root":"شيأ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَمْرُ","english":"and the Command","translit":"wal-amru","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/082_019_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/082_019_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لِّلَّهِ","english":"(will be) with Allah","translit":"lillahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/082_019_010.mp3"}]}]}
